image-plagiarism-checker/
│
├── datasets/                  # Dataset storage
│   ├── original/              # Original images
│   └── modified/              # Modified images for testing plagiarism
│
├── models/                    # Pre-trained models and training checkpoints
│   ├── pre_trained/           # Downloaded pre-trained models
│   └── fine_tuned/            # Models fine-tuned on your dataset
│
├── src/                       # Source code for the project
│   ├── preprocessing/         # Scripts for data preprocessing
│   │   └── preprocess.py      # Preprocess images (resize, normalize, etc.)
│   ├── feature_extraction/    # Feature extraction scripts
│   │   └── extract_features.py # Extract features using pre-trained models
│   ├── similarity/            # Similarity detection
│   │   └── compare.py         # Script to compare features and detect plagiarism
│   ├── web_interface/         # Web interface for users to upload images
│   │   ├── static/            # CSS, JavaScript files
│   │   │   └── style.css      # Example CSS file (if you've added any styling)
│   │   ├── templates/         # HTML templates
│   │   │   ├── index.html     # HTML template for the image upload form
│   │   │   └── results.html   # HTML template to display the plagiarism check results
│   └── utils/                 # Utility scripts and functions
│       └── helpers.py         # Helper functions
│
├── notebooks/                 # Jupyter notebooks for exploration and presentation
│   └── model_exploration.ipynb # Exploratory data analysis, model testing, etc.
│
├── tests/                     # Unit and integration tests
│   └── test_preprocess.py     # Tests for preprocessing functions
│
├── uploads/                   # Temporary storage for uploaded images
│
├── requirements.txt           # Project dependencies and libraries
├── app.py                     # Main Flask application file
├── README.md                  # Project overview and setup instructions
└── .gitignore                 # Specifies intentionally untracked files to ignore
